#### 100점 스펙 — 2. MCP 서버 MVP (Phase 1 동시출시)

```typescript
// src/app/apps/console/mcp/server.ts
// @modelcontextprotocol/sdk 사용

const server = new McpServer({ name: 'ai-console', version: '1.0.0' })

// MVP Resources (읽기전용 5개)
server.resource('clients',          listClients)
server.resource('client/{id}',       getClient)
server.resource('projects',          listProjects)
server.resource('tasks/today',       getTodayTasks)
server.resource('pipeline/summary',  getPipelineSummary)

// MVP Tools (쓰기 3개)
server.tool('create_lead',       CreateLeadSchema,       createLead)
server.tool('update_task',       UpdateTaskSchema,       updateTask)
server.tool('log_communication', LogCommunicationSchema, logCommunication)

// MVP Prompts (일상사용 2개)
server.prompt('daily_briefing',  dailyBriefing)
server.prompt('client_summary',  clientSummary)
```

**MCP 어댑터 레이어 (스펙변경 대비):**
```typescript
// src/lib/mcp/adapter.ts
export interface MCPAdapter {
  registerResource(name: string, handler: ResourceHandler): void
  registerTool(name: string, schema: ZodSchema, handler: ToolHandler): void
  registerPrompt(name: string, handler: PromptHandler): void
  start(transport: Transport): Promise<void>
}
```

**Claude Desktop 연결 설정:**
```json
// claude_desktop_config.json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "ai-console": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@ai-works/console-mcp"],
      "env": {
        "CONSOLE_API_KEY": "사용자_API_키",
        "CONSOLE_URL": "https://aiworks.kr/apps/console"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

